Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…失去了唯一的亲人姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为跟Celestial Being扯上关系  就被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝也是…姐姐也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不在了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说句话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她们两个还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会遭到Gundam的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来  我们就更有存在的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种人会进入A-LAWS里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·哈莱维  真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此你也有理由战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹  人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队和新的Gundam进行了接触
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于其是否隶属Celestial Being还尚未确认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府对此事态…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为处女座的我  从未如此地高兴过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军独立治安维持部队来迎接索玛·佩丽丝中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第五MS中队所属  安德烈·斯米尔诺夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候加入了A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有回答你的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  不  谢尔盖·斯米尔诺夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何没对刹那开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是杀了人的话  就跟你们一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该感谢刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如果不带你到这里来  你就已经被当作反联邦势力卡塔隆处死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不了解现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己所处的世界  用自己的眼睛去确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吗  把我叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆成员  莱尔·迪兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Celestial Being的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且你也将成为Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·迪兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望破坏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗拒破坏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受了种种思想  现在OO面临着战斗的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「Twin-Drive」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  驱逐Gundam的Gundam
